- segv in example3.rb

	loop 5 ...
	segv argument.rb:86

	loop 5 ...
	segv call.rb:76

	loop 5 ...
	segv call.rb:73

  add a GC.start to the loop, it works fine

  I guess we are triggering a GC at an unexpected time when things are in an
  inconsistent state


